text: Kempele is a municipality in northern Finland. There were 17,499 people living there on 31 August 2017. Kempele borders Liminka, Oulu and Tyrnävä. Kempele was founded in 1867. == Other websites == * The official Kempele page Category:1867 establishments in Finland Category:Municipalities of North Ostrobothnia
